  "texts": [
    "Specifically, as part of their decision-making processes, policymakers must collect, read, study, analyze, and process vast amounts of data.",
    "ML systems can automate the processing of large volumes of data toward extracting policymaking insights.",
    "Thus, they can help policymakers to benefit from the growing data volumes of policymaking data, without worrying about data scalability challenges.",
    "Furthermore, ML ensures that policymakers consider all relevant information via correlation and cross-analysis of multiple datasets.",
    "Therefore, there are also cases when ML models and technologies enable novel capabilities based on the identification of potentially hidden patterns and correlations of policy-related datasets."
  ],
